Midgaard's high court has approved a final writ targeting the preserve's top command after repeated attacks on bonded couriers and archive escorts. Hunt down one of the listed senior targets, with priority on the warden, and deliver completion records directly to the Proposition Exchange for magistrate review. This contract is intentionally narrow and lethal: the city wants decisive disruption, not a prolonged skirmish line.
